---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2025-01-01';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Read the Terms of Service for using Voxeia's AI voice calling platform.">
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 overflow-hidden gradient-mesh">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black font-display text-text">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose-dark space-y-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the Voxeia AI voice calling platform and related
            services ("Services"). By accessing or using our Services, you agree to these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            By creating an account or using any part of our Services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood,
            and agree to be bound by these Terms and our Privacy Policy. If you are using the Services on behalf of an
            organization, you represent that you have the authority to bind that organization.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">2. Description of Services</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Voxeia provides an AI-powered voice calling platform that enables businesses to automate outbound and
            inbound phone calls using artificial intelligence. Our Services include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-muted mt-3">
            <li>AI voice agent creation and management</li>
            <li>Automated call scheduling and execution</li>
            <li>Call recording, transcription, and analytics</li>
            <li>CRM and third-party integrations</li>
            <li>API access for custom implementations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">3. Account Registration</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li>You must provide accurate, complete registration information</li>
            <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials</li>
            <li>You must be at least 18 years old to create an account</li>
            <li>One person or entity may not maintain more than one account</li>
            <li>You are responsible for all activity that occurs under your account</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">4. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">You agree NOT to use our Services to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li>Make calls that violate TCPA, GDPR, or any applicable telecommunications regulations</li>
            <li>Engage in harassment, fraud, or deceptive practices</li>
            <li>Send spam, robocalls, or unsolicited commercial calls without proper consent</li>
            <li>Impersonate any person or entity or misrepresent your affiliation</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or access the source code of our platform</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the integrity or performance of our Services</li>
            <li>Use the platform for any illegal purpose</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">5. Billing & Payment</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li>Services are billed on a pay-as-you-go basis unless otherwise agreed in writing</li>
            <li>Prices are subject to change with 30 days' notice</li>
            <li>You are responsible for all charges incurred under your account</li>
            <li>Failed payments may result in service suspension</li>
            <li>Refunds are issued at our sole discretion, typically within 30 days of a valid request</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            All content, technology, and intellectual property in the Voxeia platform remain our exclusive property. You
            retain ownership of your data, scripts, and content uploaded to the platform. You grant us a limited license
            to use your content solely to provide the Services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">7. Service Level & Availability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We strive for 99.9% uptime for our platform. Enterprise customers may negotiate specific SLA terms. We are
            not liable for service interruptions due to factors beyond our reasonable control, including third-party
            provider outages, natural disasters, or government actions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, VOXEIA SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL,
            CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS OR REVENUES, WHETHER INCURRED DIRECTLY OR
            INDIRECTLY. OUR TOTAL LIABILITY SHALL NOT EXCEED THE AMOUNT PAID BY YOU IN THE TWELVE (12) MONTHS PRECEDING
            THE CLAIM.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">9. Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Voxeia, its officers, directors, employees, and agents from any
            claims, damages, losses, or expenses arising from your use of the Services or violation of these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">10. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Either party may terminate these Terms at any time. We may suspend or terminate your account immediately if
            you violate these Terms. Upon termination, your right to use the Services ceases immediately. We will make
            your data available for export for 30 days following termination.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">11. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any disputes arising
            from these Terms shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with applicable arbitration
            rules.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Material changes will be communicated via email or
            through the platform at least 30 days before taking effect. Continued use after changes constitutes
            acceptance of the modified Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">13. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">For questions about these Terms, contact us at:</p>
          <div class="mt-4 p-6 bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl">
            <p class="text-text font-semibold">Voxeia Legal Team</p>
            <p class="text-text-muted mt-1">
              Email: <a href="mailto:legal@voxeia.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">legal@voxeia.com</a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-text-muted mt-1">100% Remote Company</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
